title: Hatebreed - April 26 2015 - Jacksonville, Florida
description:
Hatebreed
4:05 PM
Sunday, April 26, 2015
Rockville Festival - Reverb Nation Stage
Jacksonville, Florida, USA


Band Lineup:

Jamey Jasta (Vocals)
Chris Beattie (Bass Guitar)
Wayne Lozinak (Guitar)
Matt Byrne (Drums)
Frank Novinec (Guitar)



RECORDING INFO:

Device: Sony PCM-M10
Microphone: Sony ECM-DS70P Electret Condenser Stereo Microphone
Recorded Quality: Lossless PCM
Sampling Rate: 48 kHz
Bit Depth: 24-bit
Editing: .WAV file split with Sony Sound Forge Audio Studio 9.0d LE
Conversion: EZ CD Audio Converter v3.0.6 [64-Bit]
Checksums: .MD5 & .ST5 files created with Trader's Little Helper v 2.7.0 (build 172)

Recording Comments:

Great concert, the recording came out about as perfectly as one can ask for an audience recording. I was front row, slightly left, and the sound turned out great.



Recording 'Proof' Comments:

On track 02, "To The Threshold" at 0:02-0:04, Jamey Jasta says, "Let's Go Jacksonville!". The rest of the recording has numerous other mentions to Jacksonville and the Rockville Festival.
